items.title: Awesome Ocaml
items.content_text:
### Serialization

*   [cbor (⭐24)](https://github.com/ygrek/ocaml-cbor) —  OCaml native [CBOR](https://cbor.io/) decoder/encoder.

### Testing

*   [expect-test (⭐168)](https://github.com/janestreet/ppx_expect) — A framework for writing tests in OCaml, similar to [Cram](https://bitheap.org/cram/), developed by [JaneStreet](https://blog.janestreet.com/testing-with-expectations/).
items.content_html:
